textBeforeTable: Unlike her mother Nah is extremely mature for her age and is constantly working towards being stronger and of greater use. She is proud of her manakete heritage and wants to learn all she can about what it entails. Though she does occasionally fear that being a human-manakete hybrid will cause her to become an outcast and, dislikes her rather unusual name;prefering a more common one.
